<html xmlns:o='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office' xmlns:w='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word'><head><meta charset='utf-8'><title>IELTS Answers</title></head><body><h1>DAILY ROUTINE ANSWERS</h1><h3>Câu 1: Can you tell me about your typical morning routine?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> pretty late <br>to make sure i look good.<br>when all things finished i start to go to my office. <br>and i start working.<br>the most famous vehicle in my country.<br>it is convinient and suitable for long-distance.<br>stop by (v): ghé qua (local store -> a bread, noodle or boiling cons -> bring them to my office).<br>tap water (n): nước vòi.<br>Why you do not buy any drink ?<br>Water is neccessary for my body.<br>other drink do not good for my health because they have a lot of sugar, chemistry. <br>Do you wear make up ?<br>-> use suncream, lip stick (n): son.<br>I do not like heavy make-up but natural make-up.<br>Why you do not put on heavy make-up ?<br>It takes a lot of time and money to purchase new products.<br>Cosmetics (n): mỹ phẩm.<br>What do you think about people have heavy make-up ?. <br>good at (giỏi về).<br>Do you to learn make-up in the future ?<br>In future, if i have time i will take part in makeup classes.<br>clumsy (adj): vụng về.<br>perfume (n): nước hoa.<br>heavy > < soft (adj): mềm mại.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></p><hr><h3>Câu 2: What do you usually have for breakfast and how do you cook it?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> 1. i heat (v): làm nóng the pan.<br>pour a litile oil into the pan<br>when oil is hot enough<br>i pour egg into it.<br>i wait 2 minutes and i take it out to the dishes.<br>2. How to cook rice. (rice cooker).<br>I pour rice/ wash rice and water into the rice cooker.<br>I turn on the rice cooker.<br>i wait 30 minutes.</p><hr><h3>Câu 3: Do you like going out for a short walk?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> I am bored (v_ed người).<br>leave mobile phone at home.<br>go out and walk on street. <br>Where do you often go out for a short walk ?<br>Near my house is a little park. i walk to the park from my house.<br>How far it is (bao xa) ? How long does it take ?.<br>What do you do on the park ?<br>In the park, we have many excercise equipments. take a rest and read a book.<br>What does the park have ?<br>a small lake, garden, flower, tree, grees, many chair to sit on.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br> </p><hr><h3>Câu 5: Why do you go for a walk only at the weekend?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> It allow my mind to rest.<br>i focus on physical activitiy.<br>it helps me relax and have more energy</p><hr></body></html>